media:group.media:title: i-Rocks keyboard update video (i-Rocks "v2" Clicky)
media:group.media:description:
Skip to 5:30 for a typing demonstration. 
Ermagherd, a new video type :p . Pretty surprising update from i-Rocks to their K76M Fun keyboard - a few small changes resulting in a massive difference in quality. Hope you enjoy the video!

The practice sentence was: "Hello my name is Thomas and I'm typing on the updated i-Rocks keyboard right now. This is a very nice, light-typing keyboard, I really like it! They should do more of these!"
